      "text": [
        " : رَآنِي أَبُو عَبْدِ اَللَّهِ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ وَ قَدْ تَأَخَّرْتُ عَنِ اَلسُّوقِ فَقَالَ لِي \"اُغْدُ إِلَى عِزِّكَ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3719 - It is narrated from Al-Mu'alla ibn Khunays that he said:\nAbu Abdillah (as) saw me when I had delayed going to the market, so Imam (as) said to me,\n\"Go early to your source of honor.\""
        ]
